Accounting Office and CGSO reconcile their records with the City Assessor’s Office regarding the parcels of land owned by the CGT;
Accounting Office and CGSO reconcile their records with the LTO regarding the vehicles registered in the name of the CGT;
CGSO to inform the LTO regarding the disposals made by the City for the proper dropping of ownership in its records;
CGSO to update registration of the city vehicles with the LTO;
