CGSO see to it that all government vehicles owned by the City are marked “For Official Use Only” in the manner prescribed under the GAAM and to update their registration with the LTO; and
LCE instruct concerned offices to comply with COA Circular No. 2013-004 which prohibits the display of and/or affixture of motto and symbol to government equipment, facilities and vehicles.
